items.title: 3 Reasons to Buy Floor & Decor Stock Like There's No Tomorrow
items.description: Floor & Decor's business model earned praise from an all-time great investor, and it has large expansion plans.  In 2017, home improvement retail chain Floor & Decor Holdings (NYSE: FND) went public.  Of course, that's just an expression -- there will be a tomorrow for Floor & Decor, and I believe it will be great for shareholders.

items.title: Best Stock to Buy Right Now: Costco vs. Home Depot
items.description: Costco is humming along, with solid improvement in same-store sales, membership, and new store openings.  Recently, Home Depot has dealt with a demand slowdown, but some factors could start to work in its favor.  When it comes to massive retailers, perhaps two of the businesses that immediately come to mind are Costco Wholesale (NASDAQ: COST) and Home Depot (NYSE: HD).
